## The Core Idea

Every AI content tool today solves for production volume. None solve for **compounding content intelligence** — where the system gets measurably smarter and more commercially effective with every publish cycle. That's the gap. That's the product.

---

## The 8-Stage Workflow

[1. Context Hub] → [2. GEO Strategy] → [3. Authenticity Enrichment]
↑ ↓
[8. Feedback Loop] ← [7. Performance] ← [6. Publish] ← [5. Compliance] ← [4. Generation]


### Stage 1 — Context Hub *(Gap: Shared Team Context)*
Load brand intelligence before any generation begins.
- Brand guidelines, tone-of-voice, personas
- CRM / CDP audience signals
- Competitive positioning
- Past campaign performance
- **Output:** Active Context Session that informs every downstream stage

### Stage 2 — GEO Strategy Brief *(Gap: GEO-Native Optimization)*
Plan for AI-citation visibility, not just keyword rankings.
- Topical cluster & authority gap mapping
- GEO opportunity scoring (ChatGPT, Perplexity, AI Overviews)
- Entity & schema requirement identification
- **Output:** Content Brief + GEO Opportunity Score

### Stage 3 — Authenticity Enrichment *(Gap: E-E-A-T Signal Integration)*
Inject real human expertise before generation starts.
- SME voice repository match to content sections
- Flag first-person experience injection points
- Proprietary data hooks (surveys, case studies, original research)
- Author schema auto-generation
- **Output:** Enriched Brief with SME assignments

### Stage 4 — Multimodal Generation *(Gap: Native Multimodal)*
One brief → full campaign package.
- Long-form article (GEO-structured, E-E-A-T enriched)
- Social variants (LinkedIn, X, Instagram, YouTube — platform-native)
- Email sequence
- Video script + B-roll direction
- Podcast outline
- Graphic direction prompts
- **Output:** Complete Content Package

### Stage 5 — Compliance & Governance *(Gap: Enterprise Governance)*
Nothing ships without a compliance gate.
- Industry-specific filters (healthcare, finance, legal)
- Brand voice consistency scoring
- Factual claim confidence check
- Human approval routing (configurable by risk level)
- Audit log (who / what / when / changed)
- **Output:** Compliance Report + Approval Queue

### Stage 6 — Publishing & Distribution *(Gap: Cross-Channel Orchestration)*
Push approved content everywhere, already formatted correctly.
- CMS integrations (WordPress, Webflow, Shopify, HubSpot)
- Social scheduling (all major platforms)
- Email deployment (Mailchimp, Klaviyo, HubSpot)
- UTM-tagged URLs for attribution
- **Output:** Published Content + Distribution Report

### Stage 7 — Performance Intelligence *(Gap: Revenue Attribution)*
Connect content to pipeline, not just traffic.
- Content-to-CRM pipeline attribution
- Multi-touch revenue attribution per asset
- Scroll depth + engagement scoring
- GEO citation tracking (is our content showing in AI answers?)
- Ranking velocity (traditional + AI search)
- **Output:** Content ROI Dashboard + Top Pattern Library

### Stage 8 — Feedback Loop *(Gap: Compounding Intelligence)*
Write winning patterns back to Stage 1. Every cycle starts smarter.
- Auto-identify what hooks, topics, formats, lengths drove conversion
- Update Context Hub with performance-proven constraints
- Refresh persona profiles with behavioral data
- **Output:** Updated Context Hub + Performance Playbook

