## Risk Register

| Risk | Severity | Mitigation |
|------|----------|------------|
| AI hallucinations in regulated content | High | Mandatory human review gate for healthcare/finance/legal |
| Google devaluing AI content | High | E-E-A-T engine is the direct hedge — Stage 3 is non-negotiable |
| LLM commoditization | Medium | Moat is the Context Hub + compounding data, not the LLM |
| EU AI Act (Aug 2026) | Medium | GDPR-compliant data handling + audit logs in Stage 5 from day one |
| CRM integration complexity | Medium | Start with GSC + HubSpot — highest coverage, lowest complexity |
| Adoption of Context Hub | Medium | "One-click brand scan" auto-populates from existing website (<5 min) |
| Over-engineering before PMF | Low–Med | Phase 1 ships with 3 stages only. Validate before building further. |

